<div class="row inset">
  <section class="col col-640 col-center associated-logos">
    <p><strong>In partnership with</strong></p>

    <div>
      <%= image_pack_tag("media/images/content/class-of-now/vice_logo.svg", alt: "Vice logo") %>
      <%= image_pack_tag("media/images/content/class-of-now/refinery29_logo.svg", alt: "Refinery29 logo") %>
      <%= image_pack_tag("media/images/content/class-of-now/dfe_logo.svg", alt: "Department for Education logo") %>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="col col-720">
    <p>We've teamed up with Vice and Refinery29 to celebrate the different and dynamic faces of teaching today.</p>

    <p>If you're looking for a career that allows you to bring your passions and personality to life, then teaching could be for you.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="col col-content-max">
    <%= render TextBlockWithTwoImagesComponent.new(
      heading: "Inspire future generations",
      colour: "pink",
      image_1_path: "media/images/content/class-of-now/collage-1.jpg",
      image_1_alt: "A teacher standing outside a classroom",
      image_2_path: "media/images/content/class-of-now/collage-2.jpg",
      image_2_alt: "A teacher sitting in front of lockers",
    ) do %>
      <p>
        Make a difference to young people's lives and help them to see the world differently.
      </p>
    <% end %>
  </section>

  <section class="col col-720">
    <h3>Everyday is different</h3>

    <p>Life as a teacher means constantly being pleasantly surprised by your students and their perspectives.</p>

    <h3>Grow as a person</h3>

    <p>Teaching can help you build your confidence and develop interpersonal skills, which will prepare you for wherever your career takes you.</p>

    <h3>Get rewarded for your work</h3>

    <p>A starting salary of at least Â£28,000, or higher if you're working in London, and opportunities to progress and develop your professional skills.</p>
   
   <h3> Help to get you into the classroom </h3>
   
    <ul>
      <li>
        <strong>Funding to help you train</strong> - learn more about
        <%= link_to("the options available", "/funding-and-support/") %>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>A helping hand</strong> - our advisers can offer free <%= link_to("one-to-one support", "/teacher-training-advisers") %>
        to help you decide if teaching is right for you and take the next step.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Tailored guidance to your inbox</strong> - <%= link_to("sign up", "/mailinglist/signup") %> for regular information to decide if teaching is right for you.
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="col col-full-content">
    <hr>
  </section>

</div>
